Under the new formula, we will not execute a transfer that results in more than
90% of your Account Value being allocated to the AST Investment Grade Bond
Sub-account ("90% cap"). Thus, on any Valuation Day, if the formula would
require a transfer that would result in more than 90% of the Account Value
being allocated to the AST Investment Grade Bond Sub-account, only the amount
that results in exactly 90% of the Account Value being allocated to the AST
Investment Grade Bond Sub-account will be transferred. In addition, future
transfers into the AST Investment Grade Bond Sub-account will be suspended
