Sub-account. The transfer to the Permitted Sub-accounts will be based on your
existing allocation instructions or (in the absence of such existing
instructions) pro rata (i.e., in the same proportion as the current balances in
your variable investment options). On each Valuation Day thereafter, your
Account Value will be subject to the new asset transfer formula.



