above-referenced annuities remains in effect and is not otherwise superseded.   

This supplement should be read and retained with the current statement of       
additional information for your annuity contract. If you would like another copy
of a current prospectus or a statement of additional information, please contact
us at (888) PRU-2888. This supplement is intended to amend information in the   
May 2, 2005 statement of additional information for the variable annuity you    
own, and is not intended to be an offer for any other variable annuity          
referenced here that you do not own.                                            

